Package: mnistr
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions for MNIST Dataset
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Gudmundur", "Einarsson", email = "gumeo140688@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to download, load and plot the
    mnist dataset in R. The goal is to aggregate good functions for working with
    this dataset in one package to ease the workflow for people that are new to
    working with image data in R. Some examples are given on how one can perform
    classification on this dataset and estimate performance.
License: CC0
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    caret,
    ggplot2,
    R.utils
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
